WEBVTT

00:02.127 --> 00:05.462
Starting today, I'm charging
money for food Rihoko makes.

03:36.299 --> 03:39.468
Yagi-san quit so suddenly.
What do you suppose happened?

03:39.552 --> 03:41.428
Who knows?

03:41.512 --> 03:43.639
Good morning!

03:43.723 --> 03:45.140
You're three minutes late.

03:45.225 --> 03:47.184
--Sorry!
--Amaha-kun.

03:47.268 --> 03:52.856
Unlike Takayama, I'm not going to
pay you unless you work properly.

06:27.845 --> 06:29.221
C'mon...

06:29.305 --> 06:30.931
Hey, don't ignore me.

06:31.015 --> 06:32.057
What do you want?

06:32.141 --> 06:34.935
I came to pick you up. Get in.

17:54.031 --> 17:57.408
No! I‘m going to be killed!

23:27.989 --> 23:30.783
If you want anything,
just sweet-talk it out of him!

23:30.867 --> 23:34.995
Don‘t think of him as my boss!
Let him spoil you lots!

23:35.080 --> 23:40.000
I think you‘ll both like each other a lot!
